<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-24-0149 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper examines a number of present and potential uses of lasers inthe coal mining industry. Among the applications discussed are: lasersin fiber optics communication systems; use of lasers to increase thelifetime of digging tools; laser drills; and laser sensors used to controlearth and coal removal equipment. 9 refs., 9 figs.</TEXT></DOC>